snippet.title: Game Boy Color Longplay [175] Sesame Street Sports (US)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Reinc

Sesame Street Sports is a compilation of mini-games developed by Bonsai Entertainment Corp. and released by NewKidCo for Game Boy Color and Sony PlayStation in 2001. It is based on the children's educational TV show Sesame Street.
